WEBVTT

00:02.539 --> 00:04.306
(Knocking)

00:10.792 --> 00:13.994
Hi, Johnny. Can we come in for a moment?

00:14.029 --> 00:15.395
Yes. Yes.

00:17.331 --> 00:19.733
Thank you. Hello.

00:19.768 --> 00:21.434
Oh, hi.

00:21.469 --> 00:23.336
Is everything okay?

00:23.371 --> 00:25.104
(Emotional) We've got some sad news.

00:25.139 --> 00:28.975
Uh... someone very close has died.

00:29.009 --> 00:31.844
- (Winces) Sorry.
- Oh...

00:31.879 --> 00:34.147
You remember Bob?

00:34.182 --> 00:37.150
No...

00:37.185 --> 00:39.085
