03:00.989 --> 03:02.423
(Baby wails)

03:02.457 --> 03:03.590
(Frustrated scream)

03:03.625 --> 03:05.993
(Bottle crashes and shatters)

03:06.028 --> 03:07.228
- Oh... no.
- Jesus! What the hell did you

03:07.262 --> 03:09.030
- throw that for?!
- It's still too hot.

03:09.064 --> 03:11.065
It's 20 seconds in the microwave
not 20 minutes, you tool!

03:11.099 --> 03:13.200
You've lost it. You've lost it.

03:13.234 --> 03:16.002
What the hell are you so rattled about?

03:16.037 --> 03:19.539
(Bag thumps loudly, baby wails outside)

03:19.573 --> 03:21.842
- What are you doing?
- Um, I'm gonna go stay at Ted's

03:21.876 --> 03:23.676
