me here with these people?!

03:29.817 --> 03:31.751
Yeah. Like I don't feel good about it.

03:31.785 --> 03:34.387
Um, hello! Hello!

03:34.421 --> 03:36.756
Is anybody in that hollow chest?

03:36.790 --> 03:38.358
(Baby wails outside)

03:38.392 --> 03:41.293
(Birds chirp)

03:41.328 --> 03:43.563
(Door opens, door bells jingle)

03:46.467 --> 03:49.935
Hey, Bob. How are you holding up?

03:49.970 --> 03:51.904
Oh... you know. Not bad.

03:54.741 --> 03:56.175
You know, they say death is just life

03:56.209 --> 03:58.377
except you're not here.

03:58.411 --> 04:01.146
You're somewhere else, you know? But...

04:01.181 --> 04:03.815
But that's okay because
at least you're somewhere,

04:03.850 --> 04:04.984
you know? But when does...

04:05.018 --> 04:07.219
When does somewhere become there?

04:07.254 --> 04:09.388
And when does there become here?

04:09.422 --> 04:10.655
- And I... it
- Just, just a coffee, please.

04:10.690 --> 04:11.390
- For here?
- Yeah.

04:11.424 --> 04:12.424
Okay.

04:14.593 --> 04:17.827
(Music plays quietly,
dishes and cutlery clink)

04:20.332 --> 04:22.100
(Gasps) Bob.

04:22.134 --> 04:24.769
- Hi, Johnny.
- Oh, hi... hi.

04:24.803 --> 04:27.138
You mind if I join you?

04:27.172 --> 04:28.873
I could use a little company today.

04:28.908 --> 04:31.509
