What was I supposed to do?

08:07.251 --> 08:08.884
You take his hands in yours,

08:08.919 --> 08:12.154
you look him in the eye, and say, "no."

08:12.188 --> 08:14.823
What do you say about guy
you couldn't care less about?

08:14.857 --> 08:17.593
Oh, it's Gord what's-his-name's
funeral all over again.

08:17.627 --> 08:18.827
- Who's Gord
what's-his-name? - Exactly.

08:18.861 --> 08:21.430
He was some kind of
crew-person on Sunrise Bay.

08:21.464 --> 08:24.833
I made an obligatory
appearance at the service

08:24.867 --> 08:27.503
and his hysterical girlfriend
cornered me into saying a few words.

08:27.537 --> 08:28.897
I didn't have a thought in my head,

08:28.904 --> 08:30.472
so I just stood up and sang "Danny Boy."

08:30.507 --> 08:31.839
Not a dry eye in the house.

08:31.873 --> 08:32.905
Huh...

08:32.941 --> 08:35.676
(Crickets chirp)

08:35.710 --> 08:37.345
God, I love this bed.

08:40.448 --> 08:42.549
I'm so glad you're not my brother.

08:42.583 --> 08:45.453
Yeah, yeah, I'm pretty glad about that too.

08:45.487 --> 08:48.489
But let me assure you,
tonight it is just you and me.

08:48.524 --> 08:49.723
(Happy sigh)

08:49.758 --> 08:51.058
(Kissing)

08:54.828 --> 08:57.096
(Playful giggle, gasping)

08:57.131 --> 09:00.667
(Kissing)

09:00.701 --> 09:02.602
(Panting) Um...

09:02.637 --> 09:05.838
Hey, the little guy is looking at us.

09:05.873 --> 09:09.209
Oh, yeah, dogs sometimes do that.

09:09.243 --> 09:10.910
(Kissing)

09:12.813 --> 09:14.314
(Panting)

09:16.950 --> 09:21.421
Um... maybe we could
invite it to... go? Go away.

09:21.455 --> 09:23.723
Oh, she's fine. She's fine. She's fine.

09:23.757 --> 09:25.524
(Kissing)

09:25.559 --> 09:27.994
(Collar jingles)

09:28.028 --> 09:31.163
Oh, now you want in on
the action, too, huh?

09:31.197 --> 09:34.800
Okay, the... the big one
is sniffing the diaper.

09:34.834 --> 09:36.534
Does... does that mean it's full?

09:36.569 --> 09:38.103
- Okay.
- What is... ?

09:38.137 --> 09:40.939
Okay, you guys, just give
us a little bit of time here

09:40.973 --> 09:44.209
and then you can come
sleep with us, okay? Okay?

09:44.243 --> 09:46.044
Okay, where were we?

09:46.079 --> 09:47.713
- Hmm...
- Mm...

09:47.747 --> 09:50.215
(Kissing, dogs start growling)

09:50.249 --> 09:52.483
(Barking)

09:52.518 --> 09:55.153
(Mouthing) Out! Out!

09:55.188 --> 09:58.388
(Dogs continue barking)

09:58.423 --> 10:01.826
(Loud rock music plays,
people chatter and laugh)

10:01.860 --> 10:03.961
Pass the chips!

10:03.995 --> 10:06.363
(Beer bottles clink)

10:06.397 --> 10:08.298
(Knocking) Hello. Excuse me.

10:08.333 --> 10:09.499
(Loudly) Excuse me!

10:09.534 --> 10:10.901
- Hey!
- Excuse me!

10:10.936 --> 10:13.170
- Hey! Go.
- Excuse me, hi.

10:13.205 --> 10:14.872
Oh, Buttons,

10:14.906 --> 10:16.540
I don't think you're
invited to this one, huh?

10:16.574 --> 10:18.474
I don't wanna be invited to this one.

10:18.508 --> 10:19.743
(Laughing) Hey, look
who it is. It's your dad.

10:19.777 --> 10:21.211
- He's here to take you home!
- Yeah, yeah...

10:21.245 --> 10:23.813
- Remember that?!
- Yeah! (Laughs)

10:23.848 --> 10:24.547
You remember that one?! (Laughing)

10:24.581 --> 10:27.083
No.

10:27.118 --> 10:29.152
- I'm just pumpin' your tires, bud!
- Okay.

10:29.186 --> 10:31.020
Look, what you gotta understand

10:31.055 --> 10:33.322
is that my ex-stepdad just died,

10:33.357 --> 10:35.859
so we're here celebrating his life, okay?

10:35.893 --> 10:38.261
Okay, you all seem very devastated by this.

10:38.295 --> 10:40.296
I need you to turn-mm.

10:40.330 --> 10:43.866
I need you to turn the music down, okay?

10:43.900 --> 10:47.536
