couple hours... Sleep tonight.

10:47.571 --> 10:50.906
Oh, sleep? Well, you know
who's sleeping forever, bud?

10:50.940 --> 10:52.642
- Your ex-stepdad, yeah.
- My ex-stepdad, yeah.

10:52.676 --> 10:55.210
- Yup, yeah.
- Damn, that's sad...

10:55.245 --> 10:57.012
- Okay, thank you. If you could just turn it..
- Are we out of mix?

10:57.046 --> 10:58.713
