11:00.917 --> 11:03.152
Oh my God.

11:03.186 --> 11:04.552
(Drunkenly) Don't...

11:04.587 --> 11:08.556
Oh my... (Mouths) Oh my God!

11:08.591 --> 11:10.025
I am so sorry. They got me...

11:12.162 --> 11:13.395
(Drunk whisper) They got me wasted.

11:13.429 --> 11:15.264
- Mm-hmm. - I
hate them, okay?

11:15.298 --> 11:17.432
I hate them so much.

11:17.466 --> 11:21.035
You smell... very flammable right now.

11:21.069 --> 11:23.337
Yes, I'm sure...

11:23.371 --> 11:27.374
I'm gonna need you to get
them to turn it down, okay?

11:27.409 --> 11:29.177
- Yes!
- Yeah.

11:29.211 --> 11:31.345
(Music plays loudly, Sean laughs)

11:31.379 --> 11:34.615
- Hi, Denim.
- Hi, sweetie pie.

11:34.649 --> 11:36.550
David, I so sorry.

11:49.623 --> 11:51.024
- Johnny.
- Hello, Bob.

11:51.058 --> 11:53.659
Moira, so good of you to come.

11:53.694 --> 11:56.596
